Talented Nigerian rap star, Vector has teamed up with superstar musician, Davido for a new single titled ‘Comfortable’. The song is off his Vector’s upcoming body of work, “Vibes Before Teslim“, which is expected to drop before this year runs out. The new single was produced by Vstix and Mr Eff and on the song, we have both entertainers sing about their plans to make their lovers being comfortable in their relationship. DMW boss Davido spices things up with an infectious chorus on the chant-heavy folk song, It is interesting to note that the song was teased in the thick of Vector’s public beef with MI Abaga. Listen and enjoy Comfort below: 